                     <interp inst="t18450512-1193-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 2 half-crowns the monies of <persName id="t18450512-name-951" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450512-name-951" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450512-name-951" type="surname" value="WHITE"></interp>
